name: Deliveries Package Tracker Backup
summary: An ORRS file is a backup file created by oRRs Deliveries Package Tracker, an Android app that lets users track to-be-delivered packages. It contains an encrypted record of a user's in-progress deliveries and linked delivery service account information. Deliveries Package Tracker stores ORRS files in .ZIP archives, created when a user backs up their data.
